title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-20-2013 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-20-2013 WED............PODCAST





The Glenn Beck Program





          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET
        
      
Wednesday, November 20, 2013 11:12 AM



The holidays are around the corner and Glen is excited.

  Also, Glenn's new book Miracles and Massacres is out now
 (get your copy here: http://www.glennbeck.com/miracles-massacres/)

 and Glenn loves how fellow conservative authors are climbing up the book charts
         while liberal authors nose dive.

  Plus, Brian Liley of Canada's Sun News,
      joins the show to discuss Toronto Mayor, Rob Ford's issues.
